id: Quản lý các dữ liệu khác_Count_domainmt_1

actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT mt.QuocGia, COUNT(d.ID) as SoLuongDomain
FROM MucTieu mt
LEFT JOIN Domain d ON mt.ID = d.MucTieuID
GROUP BY mt.QuocGia
ORDER BY SoLuongDomain DESC;
